# Welcome to SimplePHPSite

This is the default installation for SimplePHPSite.

Things to do now:

* adjust configuration settings in `includes/config.php` either by hand or using [admin.php](admin.php)
* <font color="red">delete `admin.php` and `includes/admin.php`!</font>
* replace the content of the `pages/index` file with your home page content
* add your other content as files in the `pages` directory
* edit the navigation links in `includes/navigation.php`
* add custom CSS to `css/custom.css`